00:20:32,494 --> 00:20:33,703
[GASPS] Oh, my God!

511
00:20:33,704 --> 00:20:35,226
Oh my God! You're here!

512
00:20:35,250 --> 00:20:37,960
Callie left me, and she went
to New York, and she took Sofia,

513
00:20:37,984 --> 00:20:39,654
and I managed to find love
again, but then she got fired,

514
00:20:39,679 --> 00:20:41,298
and I've been meaning to call
you forever, and I'm so sorry.

515
00:20:41,323 --> 00:20:43,531
Did I ghost you? 'Cause I'm...
I'm... I'm so sorry.

516
00:20:43,557 --> 00:20:45,445
I'm a terrible friend,
and I'm so glad you're here!

517
00:20:45,470 --> 00:20:46,663
[BOTH LAUGH]

518
00:20:47,585 --> 00:20:49,218
♪ I been feeling it since 1966 ♪

519
00:20:49,242 --> 00:20:50,250
Hey.

520
00:20:51,900 --> 00:20:53,410
